    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
    <link href="css/repose.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
      <button class="navbar-toggle" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".repose-navbar-collapse">
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
      </button>
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Repose Perf Tests</a>
      <div class="nav-collapse collapse bs-navbar-collapse">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li><a href="/RunningTests">Running Tests</a></li>
          <li><a href="/applications">Applications</a></li>
          <li><a href="/results">Results</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Repose Performance Tests</h1>
        <p>You'll find results for all nightly performance tests running with Repose API management software.  Every application is executed under a load test, a benchmark test, and a duration test.  Load test spins up 120% of total expected load of the application and executes for 1 hour (utilizing JMeter).  Benchmark test executes concurrent user load, starting at 20 and ending at 500.  Duration test spins up 100% of total expected application load and runs for 24 hours (this is a weekend test only).  Every test is baselined against previous tests as well as against a direct call to the origin service.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="http://openrepose.org">Learn more about repose &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="body-content">

        <!-- Example row of columns -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h2>Applications</h2>
            <p>Applications can be configured by users.  You can view application setup here and can set up/edit/delete your application.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/applications">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h2>Results</h2>
            <p>Historical results per application can be found here.  Results are split up by Repose overhead by tests (e.g. Repose duration test - origin service duration test).  Exact calls and configurations are versioned by test.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/results">View details &raquo;</a></p>
         </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h2>Running tests</h2>
            <p>Check out which tests are running and results.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/RunningTests">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <footer>
          <p>&copy; Rackspace Hosting 2013</p>
        </footer>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- /container -->
    <!-- JavaScript plugins (requires jQuery) -->
    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
